## The two projects

### dove6_server — Go fake NVR
Path: ~/dove6/dove6_server
Run: cd ~/dove6/dove6_server && go run .
Language: Go — standard library only
Endpoints: /state /health /jump?step=N /langs
Route: 18 stations Marrakech → Tanger Ville

### dove6_client — Flutter passenger display
Path: ~/dove6/dove6_client
Run: flutter run -d linux
Target: Ubuntu Linux on Aeon Gene BT06 (Dove6 screen)
Language: French default + Arabic RTL when audio synced

---

## Architecture — never change these decisions

Pattern: domain → data → presentation
DataService: abstract interface — swap NVR with one line
DisplayMapper: all routing logic lives here only
_shared.dart: all colors and shared widgets live here only
Screens: StatelessWidget — take DisplayData and bool isArabic only
No screen imports anything except DisplayData and _shared.dart

---

## Color palette — never change these

kBg         = Color(0xFFE8E4DF)  warm light grey
kSurface    = Color(0xFFD6CFC7)  card surface
kCard       = Color(0xFFD6CFC7)  cards
kBorder     = Color(0xFFC8C3BC)  borders
kPrimary    = Color(0xFF1A1A1A)  main text
kSecondary  = Color(0xFF5F5E5A)  muted text
kAccent     = Color(0xFFE8650A)  orange — main accent
kAccentGold = Color(0xFF333333)  dark grey — speed
kDim        = Color(0xFFBFB9B1)  subtle elements

---

## State machine — 10 states

idle → routeSelected → atStation → departing →
moving (speed phase 5s then progress phase) →
arriving → endOfRoute
Priority overrides: warning, manual, recovery

---

## Language behavior

French is always default.
When server sends active_audio_lang = "ar" → full
screen switches to Arabic RTL on state change.
When active_audio_lang = "fr" or "" → French.
One language per screen at a time. Never mixed.

